data.description: Check out this traditional 3-bedroom, 2 and a half bathroom home boasting a partially finished basement that serves as a family/rec room.Set on a .46-acre plot at the edge of town, this property offers a perfect blend of convenience and tranquility. Enjoy the nearby paved walking paths and a family-friendly park, just a few steps away. Inside, you'll find hardwood floors throughout and new appliances installed within the past3 years. The spacious living room features a wood-burning fireplace, while the equally large kitchen/dining area offers floor-to-ceiling cabinets and a peninsula counter that doubles as a bar/eating area, perfect for hosting large family gatherings. On the 2nd floor, you'll find 3 bedrooms, including a master suite with its own bathroom, as well as a laundry area. Outside, the property boasts a large open lawn, a newer 24x32 pole barn/garage with a work area, and a backyard patio ideal for relaxing and enjoying the great outdoors. You don't want to miss this one.
